<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
The for loop uses len as the loop counter in the second clause, but the third clause increments ptr and source in addition to decrementing len. MISRA C 2023 Rule 14.2 requires only one loop counter and that the third clause may modify only that loop counter. Modifying ptr and source in the iteration expression therefore violates Rule 14.2.
</scenario>

